  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d85\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dad\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The people of Dallas decided to separate",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the group of members of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna who supported Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma in the selection of the President will work as a separate group in the Parliament in the future.",
        "It is also said that the group includes about sixteen members of the Podujana Peramuna.",
        "It is said that the group headed by Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma will include Prof. GL Peiris, Prof. Charita Herath, Prof. Channa Jayasumana, Dr. Nalaka Godaheva, as well as the group of MPs who agree with the conscience of the Public Front.",
        "It is known that this group is also focused on building a new political movement in the future."
      ],
